# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# WeLoan365 Prototype — environment configuration
# Copy this file to `.env` (or `.env.local`) and adjust as needed.
# Vite only exposes variables prefixed with VITE_ to the app.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Base URL for app assets (icons, banners, illustrations, etc.).
#
# Leave UNSET to use the bundled static files under /public/assets
# (served at /assets/...). This is the default for local development.
#
# To stop using bundled static assets, point this at a CDN / asset server.
# Every asset reference in the app is resolved against this base, so no code
# changes are needed — just set the value and rebuild.
#
# Examples:
#   VITE_ASSET_BASE_URL=https://cdn.weloan365.com/app-assets
#   VITE_ASSET_BASE_URL=https://storage.googleapis.com/weloan365-assets
#
# VITE_ASSET_BASE_URL=
